If I understand correctly, a consequence of this change is that the record for this backfill in the bulk actions table will no longer be marked as COMPLETE until all the targeted asset partitions have either been materialized, failed, or skipped.

This means that the meaning of COMPLETE in the bulk actions table will be different for asset backfills than for job backfills.

